label: Princess Prep Back Window 3
description:
John takes the loose nail he still posesses and after a couple of tries manages to undo the latch on the window, allowing him to open it.
He climbs through  to face a basic office desk, and a couple of plants to his left and right.
One of the plants seems to be shuddering of it's own accord.

Hit 1 to continue.

Hit 0 to quit.
